{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "We remove from RELEXset all recipes with no ratings.",
    "As a result, RELEXset contains more than 180, 000 clean and formatted recipes with more than 700, 000 user ratings.",
    "One common problem with user ratings is that different users adopt different criteria and rating scales.",
    "Some users might, for example, be more tolerant than others and give higher ratings in general (Jin & Si, 2004).",
    "To mitigate this bias, following common practices in collaborative filtering models (Jin & Si, 2004), we standardize the ratings per user."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
